              "ImageDescription": {
                "value": "Red Lily at <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Capel_Manor_College\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:Capel Manor College\">Capel Manor College and Gardens</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bulls_Cross\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:Bulls Cross\">Bulls Cross</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London_Borough_of_Enfield\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:London Borough of Enfield\">Enfield</a>, <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/London\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:London\">London</a>, England.<br><b><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.capelmanorgardens.co.uk\">Capel Manor College and Gardens</a></b> in Enfield is the only <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greater_London\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:Greater London\">Greater London</a> college for 'land based' studies. The gardens, which are open to the public, are tended by students as part of course work.<br>To see the most relevant allied photos, click on <a href=\"//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Capel_Manor_College_and_Gardens\" title=\"Category:Capel Manor College and Gardens\">Capel Manor College and Gardens</a>, and this uploader's <a href=\"//commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Category:Acabashi_photos:_parks_and_gardens\" title=\"Category:Acabashi photos: parks and gardens\">Parks and Gardens</a> photos. You can find image links related to this one in a variety of ways at the very bottom of the page. This image is one of a series of date and/or subject allied consecutive photographs kept in progression or location by file name number and/or time marking.<br><b>Camera</b>: <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Canon_PowerShot_SX60_HS\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Canon PowerShot SX60 HS\">Canon PowerShot SX60 HS</a>.<br><b>Software</b>: file lens-corrected and optimized with <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/DxO_PhotoLab\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"en:DxO PhotoLab\">DxO PhotoLab 7 Elite</a>.",
